<li id="cite_note-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFWright2018" class="citation web cs1">Wright, Sarah (February 13, 2018). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.orthodoxmotherhood.com/eastern-orthodox-clean-week-traditions-tips/">"Eastern Orthodox Clean Week: Traditions and Tips"</a>. <i>Orthodox Motherhood</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">February 28,</span> 2020</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Orthodox+Motherhood&amp;rft.atitle=Eastern+Orthodox+Clean+Week%3A+Traditions+and+Tips&amp;rft.date=2018-02-13&amp;rft.aulast=Wright&amp;rft.aufirst=Sarah&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orthodoxmotherhood.com%2Feastern-orthodox-clean-week-traditions-tips%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AClean+Monday" class="Z3988"></span></span>
