</li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSirigos2019" class="citation news cs1">Sirigos, Constantine S. (March 12, 2019). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.thenationalherald.com/234518/tell-greeks-to-go-fly-a-kite-on-clean-monday-and-theyll-thank-you/">"Tell Greeks to Go Fly a Kite on Clean Monday and They'll Thank You"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/The_National_Herald" title="The National Herald">The National Herald</a></i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">March 3,</span> 2020</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+National+Herald&amp;rft.atitle=Tell+Greeks+to+Go+Fly+a+Kite+on+Clean+Monday+and+They%27ll+Thank+You&amp;rft.date=2019-03-12&amp;rft.aulast=Sirigos&amp;rft.aufirst=Constantine+S.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenationalherald.com%2F234518%2Ftell-greeks-to-go-fly-a-kite-on-clean-monday-and-theyll-thank-you%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AClean+Monday" class="Z3988"></span></span>
